          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-ai-purple transition-colors">Hosting & Maintenance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Keep your website running smoothly with reliable hosting, regular updates, backups, and ongoing support.</p>
          <span class="text-ai-purple font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1">Learn more <span class="arrow-slide">&rarr;</span></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

