          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">You know exactly what you're paying before we start. No hourly surprises or scope creep invoices.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100" data-animate>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
